==Spanish==

===Etymology===
A contraction of ''[[a cabo de]]''; ''[[a#Spanish|a]]'' deriving from Latin ''[[ad#Latin|ad]]'', ''[[cabo]]'' from Latin ''[[caput]]'', and ''[[de#Spanish|de]]'' from Latin ''[[de#Latin|de]]''.

===Preposition===
# [[alongside]], [[beside]], [[next to]]. ''(Archaic; no longer used in spoken Spanish.)''

